    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • RandomKeyFactory

        public RandomKeyFactory(int keyByteLength,
                        java.util.Random rnd,
                        java.lang.String hashAlgo)
                 throws java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException
        パラメータ:
        keyByteLength - the length in bytes of the generated keys
        rnd - the random object to be used
        hashAlgo - the algorithm to be used for digesting when generating from an array of topics
        例外:
        java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException - if the digest algorithm was not found

        public Key generate(int pow2Max)

        パラメータ:

        戻り値:

      • create

        public Key create(java.lang.String... topics)
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: KeyFactory
        Create a new key from an array of topics. If 2 arrays of topics are equals then the 2 keys generated from them will be equal If 2 arrays of topics are not equals the chances of the keys to be equal are next to none
        定義:
        create インタフェース内 KeyFactory
        パラメータ:
        topics - an arbitrary array of strings
        戻り値:
        a key corresponding to the topics array
